general.name: StarFlow_age_posterior
general.description: This file contains the full stellar age posterior probability distributions for 378,720 evolved stars in SDSS-V DR19, derived using a normalizing flow model trained on asteroseismic ages. Each row corresponds to a star, and each column represents the relative likelihood at a specific age bin in Gyrs.

hdu1.name: AGE_POSTERIORS
hdu1.description: Full age posteriors. Each column is the likelihood at a specific age; column names (e.g., 3_87 is for 3.87 Gyr) indicate the age value.
